snippet.title: Windjammers – Characters Trailer | PS4/PSVita
snippet.description:
The 6 unique characters of Windjammers will be back August 29th 2017 on PlayStation 4 and PlayStation Vita!

Windjammers is a fast-paced head-to-head arcade game where two players face off on a court, and throw discs at the opponent's goal zone to score points. The player with the most points wins.

Originally released on the NEOGEO arcade system, Windjammers perfectly blends sports and fighting games. Sharpen your throwing and sliding skills, use the best techniques to defeat your opponents, and become the world’s best player!
